Loops Basics

1. While Loop
2. For Loop
3. do while Loop
4. Break Statement

1. While Loop 

while(condition){
    // do something
}

2. For Loop

for (initialisation; conditon; updation) {
    //do something
}

3. do-while Loop

do{
    //do something
}while(condition);


4. Break Statement 
to exit the Loop

5. Continue Statement
to skip an iteration 



